node.title: Finished mobile task
node.body:
Hi Flutter enthusiasts!

Here is my solution of a mobile task.

Since I knew exactly 0 about Flutter and Dart and didn't have much spare time to learn it and also complete the task, I've of course asked mr. Chat GPT for help. Here you can find our full conversation history [https://chat.openai.com/share/b093ae6f-e16f-455c-a4d2-c2a23542111d](https://chat.openai.com/share/b093ae6f-e16f-455c-a4d2-c2a23542111d).

Unfortunatelly, Chat GPT does not care very much about things like SOLID, architectural patterns, clean code, DI and testing. So the code looks to be in a **very** rough state. But it runs and meets the requirements.

However, my goal was to finish the task in ±3 hours - I couldn't justify spending any more of my time on this. So this is what we're stuck with.
